name: Gun Club
overview:
Gun Club is a carnival rifle range type game by Genco in 1958
Put a dime in the slot then take 25 shots at moving rabbits, rotating clay pipes and foxes and other stationary targets. Score high enough and get some bonus shots.Your score gets you a grade at the end - are you an "Expert", "Sharpshooter", "Marksman" or "Rifleman"?
